# Tech Stack & Docker

**Canonical sources:** [`docs/BLUEPRINT.md`](../../docs/BLUEPRINT.md) · [`CONTRIBUTING.md`](../../CONTRIBUTING.md) §4–§7

## Docker-first gate validation

| Intent | Command |
| --- | --- |
| Smoke | `npm run docker:test:smoke` |
| Regression | `npm run docker:test:regression` |
| CI suite | `npm run docker:test:ci` |
| Lint + typecheck | `npm run docker:lint` |

## Constraints

- Pin Playwright Docker image to `package.json` version
- No hardcoded credentials — config via `.env` → `src/config/environments.ts`
- Document new env vars in `.env.example`

Full CI/CD parity rules: [`CONTRIBUTING.md`](../../CONTRIBUTING.md) §4–§5.
